<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: left;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1"><b>Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative on {!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1"><b><br></b></font></div><div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Dear {!Job_placement__c.Contact_Name__c},</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Congratulations on being appointed as {!Job_placement__c.Role__c} on NCS with The Challenge this summer on {!Job_placement__c.Wave__c}.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Your total pay for this part of the role will be {!Job_placement__c.Total_gross_pay__c}, this includes pay for &nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.Annual_Leave_entitlement__c} day(s), "Holiday Period"; per "Wave Contract", which is subject to tax and national insurance deductions.&nbsp;</span><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">We reserve the right to deduct pay for any&nbsp;</span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">unauthorised</span><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">&nbsp;absences.&nbsp;</span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">This payment will cover the following parts of the programme - &nbsp;NCS: Personal Challenge, NCS: Team Challenge and NCS: Real Challenge Design (one or more will be relevant to your role). Payments for NCS: The Real Challenge Action will be communicated to you at a later date once you have completed them.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</span></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Your payment structure for this wave is based on the principal that no one should wait longer than 5 weeks after they have completed their wave for payment therefore:-</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">1.<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>70% of the gross pay will be paid on {!Job_placement__c.Advance_payment_date__c}.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">(NB: Gross pay refers to the amount of salary that is paid to you for each wave you complete before any deductions (Tax and NI) are taken from the pay).&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">2.<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>The remaining 30% of your gross pay will be paid on {!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c} with Tax and NI deductions made from this payment.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Depending on your tax situation, this payment could be a very small amount. &nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">You will receive a separate payment email for each wave you complete.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">You will receive further information about your pay relating to the NCS Real Challenge Action weekends and Graduation (if applicable) in due course.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">This payment structure has two principles: (a) to ensure that staff members pay the appropriate level of tax in the correct month and (b) to enable staff members to receive timely payment.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Yours sincerely,</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">NCS with The Challenge&nbsp;</span></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</font></div><div><br></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">CR 2.4.2 a</font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div></div>]]></td>
